of the Duan family.

34
00:02:57,140 --> 00:02:57,660
Yes.

35
00:02:58,180 --> 00:02:59,300
He's the Young Master of the Duan family,

36
00:02:59,540 --> 00:03:00,180
Duan Xuanyi.

37
00:03:01,460 --> 00:03:02,460
His younger brother, Duan Xuanheng,

38
00:03:02,980 --> 00:03:04,460
entered Xueyue City to learn
martial arts two years ago.

39
00:03:05,620 --> 00:03:06,260
This time,

40
00:03:06,780 --> 00:03:08,140
I guess he followed his brother

41
00:03:08,580 --> 00:03:09,780
here to join the Flora Spectacle.

42
00:03:10,300 --> 00:03:11,300
It looks like the Duan family

43
00:03:11,300 --> 00:03:12,180
has high hopes

44
00:03:12,540 --> 00:03:13,540
for this Young Master.

45
00:03:14,460 --> 00:03:15,420
He's young.

46
00:03:15,580 --> 00:03:17,060
But they already passed on the fan

47
00:03:17,220 --> 00:03:18,260
and flute to him.

48
00:03:19,300 --> 00:03:20,340
He's good at martial arts.

49
00:03:21,100 --> 00:03:22,900
He has inherited the elegance of the Duan family.

50
00:03:23,620 --> 00:03:24,820
There are many ladies

51
00:03:24,820 --> 00:03:25,820
having crushes on him.

52
00:03:26,300 --> 00:03:27,060
Elegance?

53
00:03:28,260 --> 00:03:29,340
I think he's a womanizer.

54
00:03:30,220 --> 00:03:30,820
Xie.

55
00:03:35,100 --> 00:03:35,700
[Flora Spectacle]
Xie.

56
00:03:37,980 --> 00:03:38,860
How do you feel

57
00:03:39,660 --> 00:03:40,700
about seeing him again

58
00:03:41,620 --> 00:03:42,820
after so many years?

59
00:03:44,380 --> 00:03:45,420
He seems to have changed a lot.

60
00:03:46,300 --> 00:03:47,820
A person fell into the abyss

61
00:03:48,060 --> 00:03:48,980
from a high place.

62
00:03:50,100 --> 00:03:51,180
How could he not change?

63
00:03:52,660 --> 00:03:53,500
But some people

64
00:03:54,300 --> 00:03:55,580
