65
00:03:56,820 --> 00:03:58,020
[Xie Xuan, Scholarly Sword Deity]
or how many years

66
00:03:58,780 --> 00:03:59,660
he's been through.

67
00:04:00,140 --> 00:04:00,860
What kind of people

68
00:04:01,460 --> 00:04:02,420
are you talking about?

69
00:04:04,020 --> 00:04:04,780
For example,

70
00:04:06,620 --> 00:04:07,300
when I first

71
