met him,

72
00:04:09,100 --> 00:04:10,620
I thought that he was someone like this.

73
00:04:14,740 --> 00:04:15,060
By the way,

74
00:04:15,740 --> 00:04:16,340
Changfeng,

75
00:04:16,940 --> 00:04:17,940
why didn't I see your daughter?

76
00:04:20,060 --> 00:04:20,700
Don't even get me started.

77
00:04:21,180 --> 00:04:22,260
That brat

78
00:04:22,620 --> 00:04:24,580
is only interested in martial arts.

79
00:04:25,060 --> 00:04:25,700
Let's not talk about her.

80
00:04:27,380 --> 00:04:27,900
Xie,

81
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:29,780
are you satisfied with your trip

82
00:04:30,140 --> 00:04:30,820
to the Flora Spectacle?

83
00:04:31,540 --> 00:04:33,020
It's indeed a rare grand view.

84
00:04:34,100 --> 00:04:34,860
Unfortunately,

85
00:04:35,940 --> 00:04:37,380
there's no beauty in this beautiful view.

86
00:04:37,660 --> 00:04:38,740
What a shame.

87
00:04:41,460 --> 00:04:42,580
There are many scholars,

88
00:04:42,780 --> 00:04:43,780
and the walls are filled with poems.

89
00:04:44,460 --> 00:04:45,500
Without beauties,

90
00:04:46,460 --> 00:04:48,020
the brew has become bland in taste.

91
00:04:50,060 --> 00:04:51,140
Many descendants of noble families

92
00:04:51,300 --> 00:04:52,180
have gathered here today.

93
00:04:52,580 --> 00:04:54,020
Is there no one

94
00:04:54,300 --> 00:04:56,060
that captivates your sight?

95
00:04:58,580 --> 00:05:00,060
There are very few people in the world

96
00:05:00,340 --> 00:05:01,700
who can qualify as beauties.

97
00:05:02,180 --> 00:05:03,740
Xueyue City is huge,

98
00:05:05,140 --> 00:05:06,540
but I only met two beauties before.

99
00:05:07,700 --> 00:05:08,580
The first one loved gambling.

100
00:05:08,860 --> 00:05:10,940
The second one was bad-tempered.

101
00:05:11,820 --> 00:05:12,460
Besides,

102
00:05:12,900 --> 00:05:14,420
they won't come to the Flora Spectacle.

103
00:05:15,420 --> 00:05:16,020
Xie,

104
00:05:16,700 --> 00:05:17,540
you should say this

105
00:05:17,860 --> 00:05:19,700
in front of them.

106
00:05:20,220 --> 00:05:21,260
I dare not do it.

107
00:05:30,060 --> 00:05:31,300
Why isn't Airhead here yet?

108
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:32,780
I didn't expect you

109
00:05:33,180 --> 00:05:33,820
to be concerned

110
00:05:33,860 --> 00:05:35,300
about his marriage.

111
00:05:35,740 --> 00:05:36,380
I'm also concerned

112
00:05:36,540 --> 00:05:38,100
about your marriage, Lian.

113
00:05:38,420 --> 00:05:39,660
I wonder if the Fairy Rui

114
00:05:39,660 --> 00:05:40,900
has written to you lately?

115
00:05:50,420 --> 00:05:50,980
Xuanheng,

116
00:05:52,420 --> 00:05:53,100
is that lady

117
00:05:53,740 --> 00:05:54,700
your martial sister?

118
00:05:55,900 --> 00:05:56,940
I don't think I've seen her before.

119
00:05:57,700 --> 00:05:58,940
I guess she's a disciple from a noble family

120
00:05:58,940 --> 00:06:00,020
who comes to join the fun.

121
00:06:02,620 --> 00:06:03,500
When a beauty is crossed,

122
00:06:04,140 --> 00:06:05,220
the city may be turned upside down.

123
00:06:09,140 --> 00:06:09,780
It's her?

124
00:06:10,180 --> 00:06:11,540
You know her master as well.

125
00:06:11,900 --> 00:06:12,860
Qi Tianchen.

126
00:06:13,220 --> 00:06:14,540
Supervisor of Astronomy?

127
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:16,700
She is Ye Xiaoying's daughter.

128
00:06:17,300 --> 00:06:18,820
You should've met each other before.

129
00:06:21,660 --> 00:06:22,340
So it's her.

130
00:06:23,300 --> 00:06:25,300
I'll go talk to her on your behalf.

131
00:06:40,220 --> 00:06:41,660
Lian, you missed.

132
00:06:42,340 --> 00:06:43,100
Shush.

133
00:06:44,940 --> 00:06:46,540
The Invisible Water Technique
of Jiangnan's Duan family

134
00:06:46,740 --> 00:06:48,460
looks powerful.

135
00:06:50,300 --> 00:06:51,020
Don't look at them.

136
00:06:51,460 --> 00:06:52,660
Pretend that it wasn't our doing.

137
00:06:57,540 --> 00:06:58,980
Well, I didn't do it anyway.

138
00:06:59,660 --> 00:07:00,860
I think your first disciple

139
00:07:01,820 --> 00:07:03,500
has underestimated them.

140
00:07:04,100 --> 00:07:05,780
This first disciple of ours

141
00:07:05,980 --> 00:07:07,180
used to have

142
00:07:07,180 --> 00:07:08,380
a resentful look.

143
00:07:08,900 --> 00:07:10,260
He went on a trip for several months a while ago.

144
00:07:10,300 --> 00:07:11,220
He became

145
00:07:11,620 --> 00:07:13,140
more human after the trip.

146
00:07:13,820 --> 00:07:14,940
It's only been a few days,

147
00:07:15,180 --> 00:07:15,980
and he's learned

148
00:07:16,370 --> 00:07:17,340
to fight

149
00:07:17,380 --> 00:07:18,340
over a girl.

150
00:07:21,300 --> 00:07:22,020
Who are they?

151
00:07:23,020 --> 00:07:24,140
One is the eldest martial brother, Tang Lian.

152
00:07:24,740 --> 00:07:25,300
The other one

153
00:07:25,620 --> 00:07:26,980
is the new disciple of Third Master,

154
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:27,900
Xiao Se.

155
00:07:28,820 --> 00:07:29,540
Tang Lian?

156
00:07:30,140 --> 00:07:31,100
I've heard of this name

157
00:07:31,300 --> 00:07:32,020
a long time ago.

158
00:07:32,410 --> 00:07:32,940
Xuanyi,

159
00:07:33,540 --> 00:07:34,220
don't do anything rash.

160
00:07:34,940 --> 00:07:35,700
It's worth a fight

161
00:07:36,580 --> 00:07:37,900
if he's strong.

162
00:07:44,860 --> 00:07:46,140
Hey, Tang Lian.

163
00:07:47,260 --> 00:07:48,780
They said Tang Clan has a secret weapon

164
00:07:49,540 --> 00:07:50,700
called Fairy's Scattering Flowers.

165
00:07:51,100 --> 00:07:53,140
I wonder if it's like this.

166
00:07:55,580 --> 00:07:56,460
Do not attack my eldest martial brother!

167
00:08:14,780 --> 00:08:15,260
Geez.

168
00:08:16,050 --> 00:08:16,820
Like master,

169
00:08:17,020 --> 00:08:18,220
like disciple.

170
00:08:18,740 --> 00:08:19,460
His appearance

171
00:08:19,940 --> 00:08:20,860
will ruin

172
00:08:21,020 --> 00:08:21,820
my Flora Spectacle.

173
00:08:23,260 --> 00:08:24,340
Stop, Lei Wujie.

174
00:08:31,460 --> 00:08:32,460
Jiangnan's Duan family

175
00:08:33,060 --> 00:08:34,820
is no match to the Tang Clan or Lei Fortress.

176
00:08:35,540 --> 00:08:36,460
But it's kind

177
00:08:36,460 --> 00:08:37,100
of a distinguished family.

178
00:08:37,620 --> 00:08:38,820
It'll be bad if their eldest son

179
00:08:39,460 --> 00:08:40,220
dies here.

180
00:08:40,700 --> 00:08:41,460
Whoever it is,

181
00:08:41,860 --> 00:08:43,580
they can't die in Xueyue City.

182
00:08:48,780 --> 00:08:50,300
I can't control this sword qi.

183
00:09:14,540 --> 00:09:17,740
♪We accompany each other no matter where we go♪

184
00:09:18,620 --> 00:09:22,220
♪With you by my side♪

185
00:09:22,740 --> 00:09:26,180
♪It makes my youth worthwhile♪

186
00:09:26,620 --> 00:09:29,300
♪The sunset reddens your side face♪

187
00:09:29,300 --> 00:09:30,180
You've got a good sword.

188
00:09:31,580 --> 00:09:32,340
Follow me.

189
00:09:32,340 --> 00:09:34,500
♪Your gentle eyes are like jade♪

190
00:09:35,740 --> 00:09:38,820
♪Hidden within them is your tenacious faith♪

191
00:09:40,020 --> 00:09:43,380
♪A hero never sighs easily♪

192
00:09:44,180 --> 00:09:47,260
♪He'll only spend his life pacifying the world♪

193
00:09:47,620 --> 00:09:52,100
♪With his passion♪

194
00:09:52,820 --> 00:09:56,020
♪Proposing a toast to Heaven♪

195
00:09:56,260 --> 00:10:00,380
♪I cast my gaze toward the moon♪

196
00:10:00,820 --> 00:10:05,460
♪The past turns into dust♪

197
00:10:05,780 --> 00:10:08,580
♪The flowers bloom and wither
while it continues to drizzle♪

198
00:10:08,580 --> 00:10:09,780
This is the real elegance.

199
00:10:11,220 --> 00:10:11,820
This is...

200
00:10:12,740 --> 00:10:13,820
Ruoyi Sword Dance.

201
00:10:14,620 --> 00:10:15,540
General Ye created

202
00:10:15,540 --> 00:10:17,300
this dance on the battlefield.

203
00:10:18,020 --> 00:10:19,700
This sword dance is divided into two parts.

204
00:10:20,460 --> 00:10:21,900
The first part is about Celestial Gate.

205
00:10:22,700 --> 00:10:24,860
It's like fluid running peacefully.

206
00:10:26,660 --> 00:10:27,580
The second part is about Killing Array.

207
00:10:28,380 --> 00:10:29,380
The killing intent permeates the area.

208
00:10:29,900 --> 00:10:30,700
You can even sense it from afar.

209
00:10:31,420 --> 00:10:32,140
[Flora Spectacle]

210
00:10:32,140 --> 00:10:32,940
I guess

211
00:10:33,540 --> 00:10:34,740
this must be Celestial Gate.

212
00:10:35,620 --> 00:10:37,260
But there's no background music,

213
00:10:38,500 --> 00:10:39,620
it's a shame.

214
00:11:05,700 --> 00:11:06,460
What a talented player.

215
00:11:07,380 --> 00:11:08,660
Indeed.

216
00:11:09,980 --> 00:11:10,620
Sikong,

217
00:11:11,180 --> 00:11:11,980
I think I've found

218
00:11:11,980 --> 00:11:12,700
an answer.

219
00:11:14,420 --> 00:11:15,140
I'll give you

220
00:11:15,860 --> 00:11:16,540
what you want.

221
00:11:16,900 --> 00:11:17,500
Really?

222
00:11:19,220 --> 00:11:19,900
Lend me your flute.

223
00:11:24,580 --> 00:11:25,420
Scholarly Sword Deity.

224
00:11:26,580 --> 00:11:27,260
Xie Xuan?

225
00:11:28,180 --> 00:11:29,060
Don't mind me.

226
00:11:30,260 --> 00:11:30,980
It's a pleasure being able

227
00:11:30,980 --> 00:11:32,060
to watch the real Ruoyi Sword Dance

228
00:11:32,940 --> 00:11:33,780
once in my life.

229
00:11:55,620 --> 00:11:57,300
I wish to travel north with the wind,

230
00:11:58,540 --> 00:12:00,860
watching the snow sweeping across the land.

231
00:12:02,380 --> 00:12:04,060
I wish to travel east with the ship,

232
00:12:04,740 --> 00:12:07,180
seeing the elegant fairy brave the wind.

233
00:12:08,380 --> 00:12:10,300
I wish to travel far with the clouds,

234
00:12:11,020 --> 00:12:14,100
even the emperor ruling the court cannot stop me.

235
00:12:15,220 --> 00:12:17,460
I will bathe in sunlight
on the top of Mount Kunlun.

236
00:12:18,540 --> 00:12:21,420
I will witness lush mountains rise
at the edge of the ocean.

237
00:12:21,900 --> 00:12:24,660
We shall reunite after a long journey.

238
00:12:25,340 --> 00:12:28,500
But I won't go home unless I've seen the world.

239
00:12:51,500 --> 00:12:52,060
Look over there.

240
00:12:52,060 --> 00:12:52,820
-It's so pretty.
-Yes.

241
00:12:53,220 --> 00:12:53,740
It's gorgeous.

242
00:13:08,420 --> 00:13:09,300
What a coincidence.

243
00:13:10,860 --> 00:13:11,660
We met again.

244
00:13:17,020 --> 00:13:18,260
I don't know what has happened between them.

245
00:13:19,060 --> 00:13:20,060
But isn't this

246
00:13:20,860 --> 00:13:22,100
a bad opening line?

247
00:13:23,460 --> 00:13:25,020
It's awfully bad.

248
00:13:25,460 --> 00:13:26,100
Yes.

249
00:13:26,740 --> 00:13:27,420
We met again.

250
00:13:29,700 --> 00:13:30,700
A beauty

251
00:13:30,940 --> 00:13:31,820
is unforgettable.

252
00:13:32,300 --> 00:13:33,420
One day apart

253
00:13:33,940 --> 00:13:35,100
makes one long for her.

254
00:13:40,660 --> 00:13:41,740
A friend is coming over.

255
00:13:42,140 --> 00:13:42,740
Xie,

256
00:13:43,020 --> 00:13:43,820
what are you waiting for?

257
00:13:54,460 --> 00:13:55,060
Being able to meet

258
00:13:55,100 --> 00:13:56,260
the young disciples of Xueyue City,

259
00:13:57,140 --> 00:13:58,060
I only realize it stays true to its reputation

260
00:13:58,060 --> 00:13:59,020
as the First City of the Martial Art World.

261
00:13:59,700 --> 00:14:00,540
I guess this is it.

262
00:14:01,620 --> 00:14:02,660
I'll give you several books.

263
00:14:05,380 --> 00:14:06,100
This is for you.

264
00:14:07,500 --> 00:14:08,220
This is...

265
00:14:09,460 --> 00:14:10,340
Ruoyi Sword Dance

266
00:14:10,780 --> 00:14:11,540
is a good dance,

267
00:14:12,020 --> 00:14:13,420
but it's filled with a sense of hostility.

268
00:14:13,940 --> 00:14:14,700
You're in poor health,

269
00:14:14,860 --> 00:14:15,580
you can't do the dance too often.

270
00:14:16,050 --> 00:14:17,100
This dance is astonishing.

271
00:14:17,380 --> 00:14:18,140
It's like a swan goose

272
00:14:18,260 --> 00:14:19,540
soaring in the sky

273
00:14:19,580 --> 00:14:20,220
during the dance.

274
00:14:20,420 --> 00:14:22,140
It's more gentle and has less hostility.

275
00:14:22,420 --> 00:14:23,140
Thank you, sir.

276
00:14:24,260 --> 00:14:24,940
This is for you.

277
00:14:26,820 --> 00:14:27,420
Sir,

278
00:14:27,860 --> 00:14:28,660
what is this?

279
00:14:30,420 --> 00:14:31,460
Late Snow.

280
00:14:32,250 --> 00:14:33,460
This is the work of Xie Feixuan,

281
00:14:33,460 --> 00:14:34,660
a gifted female scholar from Jiangnan.

282
00:14:35,140 --> 00:14:36,060
It's very touching.

283
00:14:36,660 --> 00:14:37,980
Rumor has it that even the concubines
in the Imperial Harem

284
00:14:37,980 --> 00:14:38,860
cried while reading it.

285
00:14:40,820 --> 00:14:42,260
Learn more from the main character.

286
00:14:42,620 --> 00:14:43,820
When you meet her next time,

287
00:14:44,420 --> 00:14:45,100
don't say

288
00:14:45,100 --> 00:14:46,500
something so awkward.

289
00:14:52,540 --> 00:14:53,980
Your master always complained to me.

290
00:14:54,740 --> 00:14:55,300
He said

291
00:14:55,660 --> 00:14:56,100
he got

292
00:14:56,100 --> 00:14:57,140
a prudish disciple.

293
00:14:58,060 --> 00:14:58,700
However,

294
00:14:59,020 --> 00:15:00,860
when I heard you singing poems just now,

295
00:15:01,260 --> 00:15:01,980
you got the style

296
00:15:02,020 --> 00:15:03,300
of your master when he was young.

297
00:15:04,220 --> 00:15:05,020
This is a book for you.

298
00:15:07,180 --> 00:15:08,380
When your master was young,

299
00:15:09,180 --> 00:15:09,940
he liked to read it too.

300
00:15:10,780 --> 00:15:12,180
I've only learned martial arts from my master.

301
00:15:13,060 --> 00:15:14,420
I didn't learn how to make alcohol from him.

302
00:15:16,940 --> 00:15:17,980
You should savor

303
00:15:19,260 --> 00:15:20,180
its taste yourself.

304
00:15:22,140 --> 00:15:22,900
Thank you, sir.

305
00:15:26,500 --> 00:15:27,460
I guess you don't want me

306
00:15:28,100 --> 00:15:29,380
to call you by that name.

307
00:15:30,100 --> 00:15:31,260
But after all, you and I

308
00:15:31,540 --> 00:15:32,460
are acquaintances.

309
00:15:33,460 --> 00:15:34,260
Mr. Xie Xuan.

310
00:15:35,180 --> 00:15:36,380
Seeing that you are all laid-back now,

311
00:15:37,020 --> 00:15:38,100
I almost forgot

312
00:15:38,420 --> 00:15:39,260
that you were

313
00:15:39,260 --> 00:15:40,740
the unrestrained young man in the classroom.

314
00:15:42,220 --> 00:15:43,220
Appearances can be deceiving.

315
00:15:43,940 --> 00:15:45,260
But the zither music can't.

316
00:15:46,060 --> 00:15:47,020
I can sense your spirit

317
00:15:47,660 --> 00:15:48,700
in your zither music.

318
00:15:49,300 --> 00:15:49,900
I'm gratified.

319
00:15:50,580 --> 00:15:51,780
I don't understand what you mean.

320
00:15:52,380 --> 00:15:53,300
You don't have to.

321
00:15:54,580 --> 00:15:55,660
I'm just happy

322
00:15:56,260 --> 00:15:57,060
that I'm not wrong about you.

323
00:15:57,780 --> 00:15:58,980
This book is for you.

324
00:16:00,860 --> 00:16:01,620
I wrote it myself.

325
00:16:02,500 --> 00:16:03,660
But I haven't named it.

326
00:16:04,540 --> 00:16:05,740
If you come up with a better name

327
00:16:06,180 --> 00:16:07,180
after reading it,

328
00:16:08,180 --> 00:16:09,300
you can write it down.

329
00:16:11,540 --> 00:16:12,380
Changfeng,

330
00:16:12,900 --> 00:16:13,660
some people

331
00:16:14,300 --> 00:16:16,260
will never change.

332
00:16:16,860 --> 00:16:17,900
Thanks, Xie.

333
00:16:18,860 --> 00:16:19,340
Well,

334
00:16:20,420 --> 00:16:21,180
I'll get going.

335
00:16:22,540 --> 00:16:23,420
I just came,

336
00:16:23,980 --> 00:16:24,900
and you're leaving.

337
00:16:28,340 --> 00:16:30,060
Are you really so scared of me?

338
00:16:30,860 --> 00:16:32,090
We might as well not see each other.

339
00:16:32,740 --> 00:16:33,860
We don't have to meet in person.

340
00:16:34,420 --> 00:16:36,660
It's all in the heart.

341
00:16:37,940 --> 00:16:38,940
Stupid scholar.

342
00:16:39,580 --> 00:16:40,660
Fierce woman!

343
00:16:57,340 --> 00:16:58,060
Master.

344
00:16:58,620 --> 00:16:59,420
Good evening.

345
00:17:03,980 --> 00:17:05,300
When I was at Mount Cang,

346
00:17:07,260 --> 00:17:08,460
I suddenly saw

347
00:17:08,460 --> 00:17:09,820
a sword qi over here.

348
00:17:13,060 --> 00:17:13,780
The sword technique

349
00:17:16,660 --> 00:17:17,180
was not bad.

350
00:17:20,300 --> 00:17:20,780
Master,

351
00:17:21,100 --> 00:17:21,900
you're complimenting me?

352
00:17:23,540 --> 00:17:24,100
Having said that,

353
00:17:24,700 --> 00:17:25,620
who allowed you

354
00:17:26,260 --> 00:17:26,980
to go down the mountain?

355
00:17:35,740 --> 00:17:36,380
Master,

356
00:17:37,060 --> 00:17:38,020
how come you never

357
00:17:38,020 --> 00:17:39,020
join the Flora Spectacle?

358
00:17:39,900 --> 00:17:40,740
No matter how beautiful the flowers are,

359
00:17:41,300 --> 00:17:42,780
you'll get tired after seeing them
for over ten years.

360
00:17:43,460 --> 00:17:44,260
There's nothing more to see.

361
00:17:46,300 --> 00:17:46,780
By the way,

362
00:17:47,180 --> 00:17:47,900
was that person

363
00:17:48,180 --> 00:17:49,060
Xie Xuan who got

364
00:17:49,260 --> 00:17:50,860
the title of Sword Deity by reading books?

365
00:17:51,860 --> 00:17:53,100
He's as elegant

366
00:17:53,740 --> 00:17:55,340
and domineering as advertised.

367
00:17:57,100 --> 00:17:57,780
Stupid scholar.

368
00:17:59,300 --> 00:18:00,260
He even gave me a book

369
00:18:01,020 --> 00:18:02,580
called Late Snow.

370
00:18:03,780 --> 00:18:04,700
But the books he gave the others

371
00:18:04,860 --> 00:18:05,780
are quite special.

372
00:18:06,460 --> 00:18:07,220
I heard that the book he gave me

373
00:18:07,420 --> 00:18:08,900
can be bought
from Rustling Bamboo Book Pavilion.

374
00:18:11,260 --> 00:18:11,900
Do you like

375
00:18:12,060 --> 00:18:13,140
the girl who's called Ye Ruoyi?

376
00:18:18,100 --> 00:18:18,660
Why?

377
00:18:19,820 --> 00:18:20,660
Because...

378
00:18:21,900 --> 00:18:23,380
she's pretty.

379
00:18:25,780 --> 00:18:26,740
Is that all?

380
00:18:28,460 --> 00:18:31,900
I don't seem to have other reasons for it.

381
00:18:33,740 --> 00:18:34,540
You're quite honest.

382
00:18:35,460 --> 00:18:36,140
Master,

383
00:18:36,420 --> 00:18:37,540
I said she looks pretty

384
00:18:37,820 --> 00:18:38,620
not because I like

385
00:18:38,620 --> 00:18:40,140
all those pretty ladies in the world.

386
00:18:40,860 --> 00:18:42,380
It's just that I felt a bit weird

387
00:18:42,900 --> 00:18:43,780
the moment

388
00:18:43,780 --> 00:18:44,620
when I saw her.

389
00:18:45,540 --> 00:18:46,620
But come to think of it,

390
00:18:47,620 --> 00:18:48,700
I don't know about her past

391
00:18:49,180 --> 00:18:50,420
and her personality.

392
00:18:50,980 --> 00:18:51,900
I don't even know

393
00:18:52,100 --> 00:18:53,500
what she likes or hates.

394
00:18:54,260 --> 00:18:55,260
After much thought,

395
00:18:56,100 --> 00:18:56,900
maybe it's love

396
00:18:57,060 --> 00:18:58,340
at first sight.

397
00:18:59,380 --> 00:19:00,100
Or it's because...

398
00:19:02,220 --> 00:19:03,020
She looks pretty.

399
00:19:06,140 --> 00:19:07,300
But good-looking people

400
00:19:08,700 --> 00:19:09,500
like to cheat others.

401
00:19:11,820 --> 00:19:12,460
Master,

402
00:19:13,060 --> 00:19:13,900
does this mean

403
00:19:14,500 --> 00:19:15,820
that you've been hurt by good-looking people?

404
00:19:17,580 --> 00:19:18,260
(Master said)

405
00:19:18,820 --> 00:19:20,540
good-looking people will always cheat others.

406
00:19:21,300 --> 00:19:22,180
(It's indeed true.)

407
00:19:24,300 --> 00:19:24,980
I was wrong, Master.

408
00:19:26,780 --> 00:19:27,300
(Head down the mountain with me)

409
00:19:27,300 --> 00:19:28,100
when I come to Mount Wangcheng

410
00:19:29,140 --> 00:19:29,860
for the third time.

411
00:19:32,700 --> 00:19:33,860
I'll come again next year.

412
00:19:42,740 --> 00:19:43,460
I'll test your swordsmanship

413
00:19:44,100 --> 00:19:44,780
two months later.

414
00:19:45,860 --> 00:19:47,540
You'll become a sword deity three years later.

415
00:19:48,500 --> 00:19:49,460
This is the deal between us.

416
00:19:50,420 --> 00:19:51,260
When did we

417
00:19:51,260 --> 00:19:52,180
have such a deal?

418
00:19:52,740 --> 00:19:53,260
Mas...

419
00:19:53,980 --> 00:19:55,140
Wait for me, Master.

420
00:19:55,460 --> 00:19:57,140
Did you ask Mr. Xie Xuan over?

421
00:19:58,220 --> 00:19:58,740
I did.

422
00:19:59,780 --> 00:20:01,300
I told him about you.

423
00:20:01,740 --> 00:20:02,780
He said that lately, he's been practicing

424
00:20:02,780 --> 00:20:04,100
a kind of martial skill

425
00:20:04,660 --> 00:20:05,700
that's good for you.

426
00:20:05,820 --> 00:20:07,780
So I invited him to Xueyue City

427
00:20:08,260 --> 00:20:09,180
to teach you

428
00:20:09,900 --> 00:20:10,900
this martial skill.

429
00:20:13,820 --> 00:20:14,380
Thank you.

430
00:20:14,780 --> 00:20:15,500
You don't have to thank me.

431
00:20:17,060 --> 00:20:18,300
Xie Xuan is close

432
00:20:18,300 --> 00:20:19,020
to both of us.

433
00:20:19,860 --> 00:20:21,620
But we can't ask him to teach you

434
00:20:21,860 --> 00:20:22,820
this martial skill

435
00:20:23,260 --> 00:20:24,500
solely on account of our friendship.

436
00:20:24,820 --> 00:20:25,700
He'll only pass on

437
00:20:26,300 --> 00:20:28,060
his martial skills to those whom he thinks

438
00:20:28,660 --> 00:20:29,860
that deserve them.

439
00:20:30,500 --> 00:20:31,700
He made this decision

440
00:20:32,250 --> 00:20:33,620
right when you played the zither.

441
00:20:36,620 --> 00:20:38,260
It looks like this book can do wonders.

442
00:20:38,580 --> 00:20:39,740
After reading a few lines,

443
00:20:39,740 --> 00:20:41,460
you can already tell some tricks of it.

444
00:20:43,580 --> 00:20:44,660
The circulation of zhenqi

445
00:20:45,900 --> 00:20:47,100
can help work everything out.

446
00:20:47,900 --> 00:20:48,780
Mr. Xie Xuan

447
00:20:49,300 --> 00:20:51,380
named this martial art Circulation.

448
00:20:51,940 --> 00:20:52,740
It looks like Xie Xuan

449
00:20:53,140 --> 00:20:54,060
didn't fool me.

450
00:20:54,500 --> 00:20:56,180
He said if you practice this skill

451
00:20:56,420 --> 00:20:57,460
for three years,

452
00:20:58,260 --> 00:20:58,980
most of your power

453
00:20:59,420 --> 00:21:00,620
will be slowly

454
00:21:00,820 --> 00:21:01,580
restored.

455
00:21:01,900 --> 00:21:03,780
Combined with my medical skills,

456
00:21:04,140 --> 00:21:05,340
you might even get stronger

457
00:21:05,780 --> 00:21:06,900
than you used to be.

458
00:21:07,540 --> 00:21:08,220
But

459
00:21:08,780 --> 00:21:09,940
you must keep this in mind.

460
00:21:10,980 --> 00:21:11,540
What is it?

461
00:21:11,780 --> 00:21:13,300
He didn't mention it in the book,

462
00:21:13,580 --> 00:21:15,340
but with your intelligence,

463
00:21:15,540 --> 00:21:16,780
you'll soon find out

464
00:21:17,700 --> 00:21:18,780
that not only can the Circulation Art

465
00:21:19,340 --> 00:21:20,340
help you

466
00:21:20,500 --> 00:21:21,900
slowly restore your power,

467
00:21:22,140 --> 00:21:23,060
it can also help you

468
00:21:23,620 --> 00:21:25,900
return to your most powerful state
for a brief moment.

469
00:21:26,700 --> 00:21:28,180
But if you do this,

470
00:21:29,300 --> 00:21:30,700
everything will come to naught.

471
00:21:30,980 --> 00:21:31,620
Even your life

472
00:21:32,140 --> 00:21:33,980
will be in danger.

473
00:21:36,180 --> 00:21:37,380
Return to the most powerful state

474
00:21:37,380 --> 00:21:38,620
for a brief moment?

475
00:21:39,260 --> 00:21:40,460
Three years

476
00:21:41,220 --> 00:21:42,340
is not that long.

477
00:21:43,980 --> 00:21:44,580
Indeed.

478
00:21:46,580 --> 00:21:47,460
(I've stayed at the inn)

479
00:21:47,660 --> 00:21:49,060
(for more than three years.)

480
00:21:55,900 --> 00:21:57,580
But the word magical power

481
00:21:57,940 --> 00:22:00,980
shows that magic and power are reciprocal.

482
00:22:01,700 --> 00:22:02,460
What is power?

483
00:22:03,540 --> 00:22:04,180
Power

484
00:22:04,580 --> 00:22:05,660
means your heart.

485
00:22:06,020 --> 00:22:08,060
Physical diseases are curable.

486
00:22:08,780 --> 00:22:09,940
But what about psychological diseases?

487
00:22:10,940 --> 00:22:11,500
I know.

488
00:22:11,900 --> 00:22:13,860
That incident has brought you great harm.

489
00:22:14,380 --> 00:22:15,500
But I really hope

490
00:22:16,420 --> 00:22:17,860
you could stay strong and get over it.

491
00:22:21,380 --> 00:22:21,980
Father.

492
00:22:23,820 --> 00:22:24,220
Qianluo.

493
00:22:24,380 --> 00:22:25,020
Father,

494
00:22:25,540 --> 00:22:26,460
why did you end the Flora Spectacle

495
00:22:26,700 --> 00:22:27,620
before I came?

496
00:22:28,180 --> 00:22:28,940
You brat.

497
00:22:29,420 --> 00:22:30,340
You ignored me when I asked

498
00:22:30,340 --> 00:22:31,060
you to come.

499
00:22:31,460 --> 00:22:32,610
Now that everyone has left,

500
00:22:32,700 --> 00:22:34,180
you blame us for ending it too soon.

501
00:22:34,500 --> 00:22:35,220
Geez, you brat.

502
00:22:35,540 --> 00:22:36,380
I heard

503
00:22:36,460 --> 00:22:37,740
that Mr. Scholarly Sword Deity came too.

504
00:22:38,100 --> 00:22:38,580
He even gave

505
00:22:38,740 --> 00:22:39,660
everyone a book as a gift.

506
00:22:40,220 --> 00:22:40,860
Where's mine?

507
00:22:41,300 --> 00:22:41,940
Yours?

508
00:22:42,860 --> 00:22:44,380
Of course you have one.

509
00:22:44,780 --> 00:22:46,300
He asked me to give you this.

510
00:22:53,860 --> 00:22:54,580
This brat said

511
00:22:54,580 --> 00:22:56,180
the spear techniques I passed on to her

512
00:22:56,220 --> 00:22:56,940
were too manly.

513
00:22:57,140 --> 00:22:58,060
So she clamored for it.

514
00:22:58,380 --> 00:22:59,380
Look, look.

515
00:22:59,940 --> 00:23:00,500
Father.

516
00:23:06,860 --> 00:23:07,620
Yanhui,

517
00:23:08,260 --> 00:23:10,060
you've done great all these years.

518
00:23:11,340 --> 00:23:13,780
Great Elder, please get to the point.

519
00:23:14,140 --> 00:23:14,940
All these years,

520
00:23:15,340 --> 00:23:16,900
from the fall to the rise

521
00:23:17,100 --> 00:23:18,500
of Wushuang City,

522
00:23:19,020 --> 00:23:21,580
it's all thanks to your contribution.

523
00:23:22,020 --> 00:23:23,700
You have the talent to revive a country.

524
00:23:24,140 --> 00:23:24,780
But

525
00:23:25,060 --> 00:23:26,860
what Wushuang City needs now

526
00:23:27,020 --> 00:23:29,580
is a person who can expand the territory.

527
00:23:31,660 --> 00:23:33,180
An ambitious person?

528
00:23:34,300 --> 00:23:34,860
Yes.

529
00:23:35,860 --> 00:23:38,700
From now on, you don't have to worry

530
00:23:39,140 --> 00:23:40,620
about the affairs in the city.

531
00:23:42,100 --> 00:23:44,020
Leave it to Songtao.

532
00:23:44,940 --> 00:23:45,620
Yanhui,

533
00:23:46,420 --> 00:23:47,220
long time no see.

534
00:23:48,900 --> 00:23:50,660
I was never interested in the position

535
00:23:51,300 --> 00:23:52,020
of the City Lord

536
00:23:52,020 --> 00:23:52,820
of Wushuang City.

537
00:23:54,340 --> 00:23:54,940
But

538
00:23:55,460 --> 00:23:56,180
Songtao

539
00:23:57,180 --> 00:23:58,340
is ineligible to take this position.

540
00:23:58,660 --> 00:23:59,620
What did you say?

541
00:24:00,860 --> 00:24:02,260
Songtao's martial skills were not

542
00:24:02,380 --> 00:24:03,300
as good as mine.

543
00:24:04,220 --> 00:24:05,860
That's why he left Wushuang City.

544
00:24:06,660 --> 00:24:08,500
Now that you ask him back,

545
00:24:09,060 --> 00:24:10,020
it's just because

546
00:24:10,460 --> 00:24:11,580
it's easier to control him.

547
00:24:12,420 --> 00:24:13,700
He'll obey your orders

548
00:24:13,900 --> 00:24:14,820
and do what he is told.

549
00:24:15,700 --> 00:24:16,500
Yanhui,

550
00:24:17,340 --> 00:24:18,380
you've crossed the line.

551
00:24:19,300 --> 00:24:20,940
I can quit being the City Lord.

552
00:24:22,100 --> 00:24:23,340
But I'd like to recommend someone.

553
00:24:24,620 --> 00:24:25,860
I guess I have this right, don't I?

554
00:24:27,060 --> 00:24:27,860
Of course.

555
00:24:28,460 --> 00:24:29,420
You mean this kid?

556
00:24:30,220 --> 00:24:31,500
A brat like you

557
00:24:31,780 --> 00:24:33,100
wants to be the City Lord?

558
00:24:33,420 --> 00:24:34,500
You must fight me before that.

559
00:24:34,940 --> 00:24:36,260
He's indeed a little kid.

560
00:24:36,980 --> 00:24:37,740
Wushuang!

561
00:24:39,020 --> 00:24:40,140
Coming, Master.

562
00:24:49,660 --> 00:24:51,260
Wushuang Sword Box?

563
00:24:55,740 --> 00:24:57,420
It's you, little brat?

564
00:24:58,140 --> 00:24:58,660
Mister,

565
00:24:59,260 --> 00:25:00,020
who are you?

566
00:25:03,860 --> 00:25:05,140
I'm Ye Songtao.

567
00:25:09,300 --> 00:25:11,220
I don't think you are that well-known.

568
00:25:11,420 --> 00:25:11,820
You...

569
00:25:11,820 --> 00:25:12,900
He's not well-known.

570
00:25:13,540 --> 00:25:15,220
You're right this time.

571
00:25:16,050 --> 00:25:16,620
Wushuang,

572
00:25:17,900 --> 00:25:19,420
next, you'll have to battle

573
00:25:19,700 --> 00:25:20,580
with your martial uncle.

574
00:25:21,900 --> 00:25:22,900
If you win,

575
00:25:23,540 --> 00:25:24,020
you'll be

576
00:25:24,020 --> 00:25:25,300
the City Lord of Wushuang City.

577
00:25:25,980 --> 00:25:27,180
Okay, I understand.

578
00:25:29,980 --> 00:25:30,780
