698
00:32:36,060 --> 00:32:36,620
Sure.

699
00:32:37,140 --> 00:32:38,180
I'll show you a technique as well.

700
00:32:39,060 --> 00:32:40,260
It also has a name.

701
00:32:40,980 --> 00:32:42,380
It's called Astonishing Thunder.

702
00:33:02,500 --> 00:33:03,100
Nice defense.

703
00:33:04,380 --> 00:33:05,500
But I guess this was meant to be

704
00:33:06,460 --> 00:33:07,620
the third technique

