00:33:59,500 --> 00:34:00,540
Bent your right leg more.

714
00:34:01,340 --> 00:34:02,100
Eyes straight ahead.

715
00:34:02,580 --> 00:34:03,260
Good.

716
00:34:03,900 --> 00:34:04,700
Sancai Sword Technique.

