Hanyi.

724
00:34:55,660 --> 00:34:56,580
You're a crybaby as always.

725
00:35:03,540 --> 00:35:04,140
Jie,

726
00:35:05,700 --> 00:35:06,300
you've suffered

727
00:35:08,060 --> 00:35:08,740
