728
00:35:50,340 --> 00:35:50,980
Third Master,

729
00:35:51,740 --> 00:35:52,500
what's going on?

730
00:35:53,460 --> 00:35:54,420
Just now, Second Master...

731
00:36:00,540 --> 00:36:01,700
Hanyi entered the sect

732
00:36:01,700 --> 00:36:02,860
a month earlier than me.

733
00:36:03,260 --> 00:36:03,940
But in fact,

734
00:36:05,100 --> 00:36:06,460
she's four years younger than me.

735
00:36:07,140 --> 00:36:07,940
Her mother

736
00:36:08,300 --> 00:36:09,860
is Li Xinyue, the heiress of Sword Tomb.

737
00:36:10,380 --> 00:36:13,100
Her father is Lei Mengsha of the Lei Clan.

738
00:36:14,740 --> 00:36:15,660
She didn't join the Lei Clan,

739
00:36:16,100 --> 00:36:16,940
so she took her mother's family name.

740
00:36:21,540 --> 00:36:21,980
Your Highness,

741
00:36:22,380 --> 00:36:23,020
please don't make things hard for us.

742
00:36:23,580 --> 00:36:24,180
His Majesty has given his order.

743
00:36:24,540 --> 00:36:25,820
If you insist on getting out of here,

744
00:36:26,540 --> 00:36:27,780
