745
00:36:28,420 --> 00:36:29,500
We can execute you before notifying His Majesty.

746
00:36:30,340 --> 00:36:31,780
You can't stop me.

747
00:36:32,540 --> 00:36:33,780
We know you're a martial arts expert.

748
00:36:34,500 --> 00:36:35,380
But we're fearless.

749
00:36:36,460 --> 00:36:37,420
You'll have to go out

750
00:36:37,820 --> 00:36:39,460
over our dead bodies.

751
00:36:39,980 --> 00:36:41,180
Then, try me.

752
00:36:41,420 --> 00:36:42,300
Wait, Your Highness.

753
00:36:45,780 --> 00:36:46,900
[Li Xinyue, Guardian Azure Dragon]

754
00:36:46,900 --> 00:36:47,340
Your Highness,

755
00:36:47,620 --> 00:36:48,380
due to your special status,

756
00:36:48,620 --> 00:36:49,660
you can't go to the execution ground.

757
00:36:50,340 --> 00:36:51,140
Aunt Xinyue,

758
00:36:51,980 --> 00:36:53,020
why are you stopping me too?

759
00:36:53,380 --> 00:36:53,940
No.

760
00:36:55,500 --> 00:36:56,380
Leave this to me.

761
00:36:57,220 --> 00:36:58,500
I'll go get His Highness back.

762
00:36:58,940 --> 00:36:59,620
Trust me.

763
00:37:06,140 --> 00:37:06,820
One of the Four Heroes of the Lei Clan,

764
00:37:07,300 --> 00:37:07,940
Lei Mengsha?

765
00:37:30,620 --> 00:37:31,180
Xiao Se,

766
00:37:32,020 --> 00:37:32,780
why are you staring vacantly into space?

767
00:37:34,180 --> 00:37:35,100
Something

768
00:37:37,420 --> 00:37:38,780
is really predestined.

769
00:37:46,540 --> 00:37:47,060
Hanyi,

770
00:37:47,860 --> 00:37:48,660
this is...

771
00:37:50,860 --> 00:37:52,340
This is Mother's Azure Dragon Token.

772
00:37:53,860 --> 00:37:54,620
Twenty years ago,

773
00:37:55,500 --> 00:37:57,660
Mother and Father attacked Pingqing Hall

774
00:37:58,180 --> 00:37:59,220
while protecting the Emperor.

775
00:38:00,380 --> 00:38:01,100
Then, Father

776
00:38:01,780 --> 00:38:02,980
was appointed as one of the Eight Pillars

777
00:38:03,740 --> 00:38:04,780
and served in the expedition against Nanjue.

778
00:38:06,180 --> 00:38:07,220
He died on the battlefield.

779
00:38:07,860 --> 00:38:10,220
Mother and the other three martial arts people

780
00:38:10,460 --> 00:38:11,860
who refused to be officials

781
00:38:12,620 --> 00:38:13,580
were granted the vanity title

782
00:38:13,740 --> 00:38:14,860
of Tianqi's Four Guardians.

783
00:38:15,540 --> 00:38:16,620
[Azure Dragon]
Mother was posted at East.

784
00:38:17,340 --> 00:38:18,220
Her code name was Azure Dragon.

785
00:38:19,620 --> 00:38:20,700
Azure Dragon?

786
00:38:21,620 --> 00:38:23,180
It sounds very strong.

787
00:38:23,980 --> 00:38:24,740
I once

788
00:38:25,660 --> 00:38:26,700
hated this token.

789
00:38:27,740 --> 00:38:28,380
Because I thought

790
00:38:28,380 --> 00:38:29,420
it was this token

791
00:38:30,540 --> 00:38:31,580
that got our mother killed.

792
00:38:33,540 --> 00:38:34,940
But after all, this is Mother's relic.

793
00:38:35,660 --> 00:38:36,460
About Mother,

794
00:38:37,340 --> 00:38:38,900
my master refused to tell me in detail.

795
00:38:39,820 --> 00:38:40,580
I heard it

796
00:38:40,580 --> 00:38:41,260
from the others.

797
00:38:42,500 --> 00:38:43,460
But I don't know

798
00:38:44,500 --> 00:38:45,060
why Mother

799
00:38:45,060 --> 00:38:46,420
would leave me all alone

800
00:38:47,380 --> 00:38:48,420
at Lei Fortress

801
00:38:50,620 --> 00:38:51,540
when I was a kid.

802
00:38:52,300 --> 00:38:53,660
That's because Mother was used

803
00:38:53,660 --> 00:38:55,460
to witnessing the conspiracy in Tianqi City.

804
00:38:56,100 --> 00:38:56,620
She didn't want

805
00:38:56,620 --> 00:38:58,100
you to grow up in such an environment.

806
00:38:59,420 --> 00:39:00,220
She wanted you

807
00:39:01,860 --> 00:39:03,220
to return to the martial arts world

808
00:39:04,780 --> 00:39:05,900
and grow up freely

809
00:39:07,340 --> 00:39:08,300
while staying away from disputes.

810
00:39:09,620 --> 00:39:10,460
Was that so?

811
00:39:11,300 --> 00:39:12,180
Or maybe

812
00:39:12,980 --> 00:39:14,380
Mother could foresee

813
00:39:16,290 --> 00:39:17,420
the coming of that day.

814
00:39:20,140 --> 00:39:20,980
What had exactly happened?

815
00:39:22,580 --> 00:39:23,420
After Mother

816
00:39:23,420 --> 00:39:24,740
was appointed as one of Tianqi's Four Guardians,

817
00:39:25,140 --> 00:39:26,140
she had been working hard

818
00:39:26,380 --> 00:39:27,140
to protect the imperial city.

819
00:39:28,020 --> 00:39:28,820
Until that year,

820
00:39:29,700 --> 00:39:30,500
(Lord Langya's alleged treason)

821
00:39:30,500 --> 00:39:32,060
(shocked everyone in the country.)

822
00:39:32,740 --> 00:39:34,500
(Lord Langya used to be
the backbone of the country.)

823
00:39:35,180 --> 00:39:36,140
(He helped Beili to repel)

824
00:39:36,140 --> 00:39:37,180
(the invasion of Nanjue many times.)

825
00:39:38,300 --> 00:39:40,060
(He was the big hero who everyone admired.)

826
00:39:41,420 --> 00:39:42,580
But he was suddenly imprisoned.

827
00:39:43,300 --> 00:39:44,020
He was convicted

828
00:39:45,460 --> 00:39:46,340
of treason.

829
00:39:48,060 --> 00:39:49,140
Did he do it?

830
00:39:49,580 --> 00:39:51,020
No one believed that it was true.

831
00:39:51,820 --> 00:39:54,100
But ever since he was imprisoned,

832
00:39:54,620 --> 00:39:55,740
Lord Langya had remained silent.

833
00:39:56,500 --> 00:39:57,820
He had never spoken a word.

834
00:39:58,380 --> 00:39:59,140
He didn't admit it

835
00:39:59,700 --> 00:40:00,900
(or defend himself.)

836
00:40:02,300 --> 00:40:04,180
(Among Tianqi's Seven Censors
who interrogated him,)

837
00:40:04,460 --> 00:40:05,860
(three of them reckoned he was innocent.)

838
00:40:06,540 --> 00:40:07,260
(But on the next day,)

839
00:40:07,860 --> 00:40:09,260
(they were found dead at their houses.)

840
00:40:10,220 --> 00:40:11,940
Emperor Mingde wanted him dead.

841
00:40:12,900 --> 00:40:14,180
So no reason was needed.

842
00:40:15,260 --> 00:40:16,370
It didn't even need evidence.

843
00:40:17,020 --> 00:40:17,580
But that day

844
00:40:17,580 --> 00:40:18,740
when he was executed...

845
00:40:20,100 --> 00:40:20,660
What happened?

846
00:40:25,620 --> 00:40:26,860
[Execute]

847
00:41:02,220 --> 00:41:02,740
Your Highness.

848
00:41:03,420 --> 00:41:06,100
[Xiao Ruofeng, Lord Langya]

849
00:41:06,340 --> 00:41:06,980
Who are you?

850
00:41:08,980 --> 00:41:10,260
Azure Dragon?

851
00:41:11,100 --> 00:41:11,820
Li Xinyue?

852
00:41:14,220 --> 00:41:14,980
Mother showed up.

